Package au.csiro.pathling.fhirpath

Interface FhirPath

All Known Subinterfaces:
Literals.LiteralPath, ParserPaths.ValuePath<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
FhirPath.Composite, FhirPath.This, Literals.BooleanLiteral, Literals.CodingLiteral, Literals.DecimalLiteral, Literals.IntegerLiteral, Literals.NullLiteral, Literals.StringLiteral, ParserPaths.TypeNamespacePath, ParserPaths.TypeSpecifierPath, Paths.EvalFunction, Paths.EvalOperator, Paths.EvalUnaryOperator, Paths.ExternalConstantPath, Paths.Resource, Paths.Traversal
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public interface FhirPath
A description of how to take one Collection and transform it into another.
Author:
John Grimes
